sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User writes a new note and presses save button in SPA

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    
    Note right of server: Server processes the new note and saves it
    
    server-->>browser: HTTP 201 Created { "content": new note", "date": "2024-04-27" }
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of browser: Browser updates the note list without reloading the page
    
    browser->>browser: Render the new note in the SPA view
